{"tid":2393053,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"2018年反東大嶼論壇衝突 警事隔兩年再拘3人 2月18日上午東區法院提堂","createTime":"2021-02-03T07:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T11:02:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3374548ecb61cc2a14a51d2baff8e14823ded6fb","tid":2393053,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T07:56:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F5128&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=4ac24d8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5128</a><br />\n<br />\n【東方日報】土地公義聯合陣線、守護大嶼聯盟於2018年10月14日發起「反對東大嶼填海人工島遊行」，當日遊行人士由銅鑼灣東角道遊行至政府總部，其後在俗稱「公民廣場」的政府總部東翼前地舉行論壇，至晚上約7時20分一度爆發混亂，逾10名身穿黑衣、戴口罩的「黑衣人」衝到台上「搶咪」，又揮拳攻擊主持人和參與的市民。<br />\n<br />\n港島總區刑事部公眾活動調查組其後接手跟進案件，經進一步調查，人員今日(3日)上午約7時分別在紅磡、長沙灣及將軍澳區拘捕3名本地男子，年齡介乎18至28歲。3名被捕男子已各被控一項「參與非法集結」罪，其中一人同時被控一項「普通襲擊」罪，案件將於本月18日上午在東區裁判法院提堂。（全文）<br />\n<br />\n#20210203新聞"},{"pid":"45af991d7affb438bbee6c7d2924b927a41dddea","tid":2393053,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17175e295a5f4a449aef29d2cf5b718165907fb","tid":2393053,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2018都拉"},{"pid":"16c383451db8d853e3e870c5d58cde4123c7fc70","tid":2393053,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:05:33.000Z","msg":"紅媒好撚鍾意強調黑衣.."},{"pid":"ba9643a0c4987d35022c285d9d36f98570661239","tid":2393053,"uid":49329,"lik